NAME
       clear - clear the terminal screen

SYNOPSIS
       clear

DESCRIPTION
       clear clears your screen if this is possible.  It looks in
       the environment for the terminal type and then in the ter­
       minfo database to figure out how to clear the screen.

SEE ALSO
       tput(1), terminfo(5)



